    </stitle>
    <svcsection/>
    <svcproc svcproctype="check" graphiccount="0">
        <title>PROPER OPERATION CHECK</title>
        <para>At 90 day intervals, the drive axles should be raised and the NoSPIN differential checked (refer to
            <hotlnk document="s14003_15.xml" xrefid="hl1400303">OPERATION TEST
                <xref refid="hl1400303"/>
            </hotlnk>
            ) to be sure it is operating properly. This test will also determine if both axle shafts are intact.
        </para>
